g class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/72be13b1306477dafde48f3288cfb360.webp?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/72be13b1306477dafde48f3288cfb360.webp?t=1737043394 width=800 height=17 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/5e2dee6ad2142101471230802223e136.poster.avif?t=1737043394\" width=800 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/5e2dee6ad2142101471230802223e136.webm?t=1737043394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/5e2dee6ad2142101471230802223e136.mp4?t=1737043394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/5b4326e34ca8bb8eaa6dd589fcbd4112.webp?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/5b4326e34ca8bb8eaa6dd589fcbd4112.webp?t=1737043394 width=800 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/6b99c67abae6e11ef4abccf0dbb054d0.avif?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/6b99c67abae6e11ef4abccf0dbb054d0.avif?t=1737043394 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hundreds of unique, high quality paintings</strong> created  exclusively for Gallery. Original gameplay: combination of coloring book and home design! Color pictures, get stars and spend them on decorating the house and exploring the story. That’s a creative game for real designers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/72be13b1306477dafde48f3288cfb360.webp?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/72be13b1306477dafde48f3288cfb360.webp?t=1737043394 width=800 height=17 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/a21612d5de7e3d702f61f58ace00316c.poster.avif?t=1737043394\" width=800 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/a21612d5de7e3d702f61f58ace00316c.webm?t=1737043394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/a21612d5de7e3d702f61f58ace00316c.mp4?t=1737043394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/5b4326e34ca8bb8eaa6dd589fcbd4112.webp?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/5b4326e34ca8bb8eaa6dd589fcbd4112.webp?t=1737043394 width=800 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/a984cf8c6de82b3496c87ca4296c0d90.avif?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/a984cf8c6de82b3496c87ca4296c0d90.avif?t=1737043394 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A variety of locations to explore and to renovate.</strong> We have a cozy corner for every taste here! Rich and variable decor: there is always more than one option to pick for each and every corner of the house and other locations as well!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/72be13b1306477dafde48f3288cfb360.webp?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/72be13b1306477dafde48f3288cfb360.webp?t=1737043394 width=800 height=17 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/edf1c8ce448d63e117de40621be050e1.poster.avif?t=1737043394\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/edf1c8ce448d63e117de40621be050e1.webm?t=1737043394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/edf1c8ce448d63e117de40621be050e1.mp4?t=1737043394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/5b4326e34ca8bb8eaa6dd589fcbd4112.webp?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/5b4326e34ca8bb8eaa6dd589fcbd4112.webp?t=1737043394 width=800 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/4c4f8274153e73678e47a47a28df392c.avif?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/4c4f8274153e73678e47a47a28df392c.avif?t=1737043394 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wide range of outfits for the main heroes</strong>, Mia and Leo. Want to see Mia as an ancient princess, a movie-star or a race track mechanic? Sure thing! Want Leo to be a giant turkey, a dancer or a fireman? We’ve got it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/72be13b1306477dafde48f3288cfb360.webp?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/72be13b1306477dafde48f3288cfb360.webp?t=1737043394 width=800 height=17 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/f82361d231cdc05b56a3a4fa335567ef.poster.avif?t=1737043394\" width=800 height=396 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/f82361d231cdc05b56a3a4fa335567ef.webm?t=1737043394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/f82361d231cdc05b56a3a4fa335567ef.mp4?t=1737043394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/5b4326e34ca8bb8eaa6dd589fcbd4112.webp?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/5b4326e34ca8bb8eaa6dd589fcbd4112.webp?t=1737043394 width=800 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/a9f25e47b081538f8300d52085f517bf.avif?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/a9f25e47b081538f8300d52085f517bf.avif?t=1737043394 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You can't lose here!</strong> No 'Game over' signs! All you have to do here is color pictures, relax and enjoy the story. We have numerous in-game events waiting for our players where you can get new exclusive paintings to color, decor elements to instal and pets to… well, to pet!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In short - grab a brush, get comfy and let’s paint that world bright!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/5b4326e34ca8bb8eaa6dd589fcbd4112.webp?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/5b4326e34ca8bb8eaa6dd589fcbd4112.webp?t=1737043394 width=800 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/fccb0e1060a3aebc646050dc3511e45c.avif?t=1737043394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras_big/fccb0e1060a3aebc646050dc3511e45c.avif?t=1737043394 width=800 height=53 /></span></p>",
